sonobuoy-config.description: An easy to start from project for making K8s aware tests.

spec.name: plugin
args: /kube/kubectl-mtb_linux_amd64 run benchmarks -n "test" --as "system:serviceaccount:default:divya"; mkdir -p /tmp/sonobuoy/results; cp /tmp/mtlb.json /tmp/sonobuoy/results/; tar czvf /tmp/sonobuoy/results/results.tar.gz -C /tmp/sonobuoy/results/ .; echo -n /tmp/sonobuoy/results/results.tar.gz > /tmp/sonobuoy/results/done
